data.description: Nestled on a generous 9-acre parcel in the coveted ACID irrigation district, this property is a slice of rural paradise. A spacious 3-bedroom, 2-bath home welcomes you with vaulted ceilings, gas fireplace, and open room concept. The kitchen includes a walk-in pantry, newer stainless steel appliances and beautiful granite countertops. You'll have plenty of space for projects, storage, toys and more with the attached 3-car garage and the separate 20'X24' detached 2-car garage/shop. The 3-stall barn includes a tack room, hay loft, and lighting. The irrigated pasture has yielded 3 cuttings of 200-100# bails.  Tucked away on a private road, this tranquil retreat offers the perfect blend of space, comfort, and a rural lifestyle. Don't miss this opportunity to call 21893 Spoon Ln your own!
